These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk, sprite, lemonade
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, reading, puzzles, baking
1. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person drinking milk and the person who's hobby is reading##2
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is video-games##3
3. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere between the person drinking lemonade and the person drinking milk##7
4. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
6. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | sprite | lemonade       | soy-milk | milk        |
| Hobby      | puzzles  | reading | baking        | video-games |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: pony, turtle, rabbit, fish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, weightlifting, water-polo, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is somewhere between the person who's sport is water-polo and the owner of the rabbit##7
2. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5
3. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skiing##5
4. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
5. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | rabbit | turtle       | fish         | pony     |
| Sport   | weightlifting   | skiing | water-polo | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, drama, satire, epic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, reggae, metal, rock
1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the fan of rock##1
2. the fan of rock is somewhere between the fan of reggae and the fan of folk##7
3. the fan of metal is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the fan of folk is somewhere between the fan of rock and the person watching drama movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | epic | satire | western  |
| Music-Genre   | metal | folk  | rock   | reggae |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, baking, singing, filmmaking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, biathlon, cycling, swimming
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##7
3. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | baking | chess | filmmaking       | singing |
| Sport   | biathlon      | basketball   | cycling | swimming  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, board-games, skydiving, card-games
There are 4 different nationalities: french, mexican, canadian, indian
1. the indian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is board-games##3
2. the french is somewhere to the left of the mexican##5
3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the indian is somewhere between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is traveling##7
5. the indian is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the mexican is somewhere to the left of the indian##5
7. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | traveling   | card-games | board-games |
| Nationality   | french      | mexican | indian      | canadian |

