.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, hot-chocolate, soy-milk, fanta
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, argentine, french, mexican
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the french##1
2. the french is the person drinking fanta##1
3. the argentine is on the right of the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the mexican##3
6. the mexican is somewhere between the brazilian and the argentine##7
7. the french is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | water      | soy-milk | fanta     |
| Nationality   | brazilian    | mexican | argentine   | french |

