.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: potato, garlic, apple, plum
There are 4 different nationalities: german, russian, polish, indian
1. the german is on the far left##1
2. the person eating garlic is on the left of the russian##1
3. the person eating plum is on the far left or far right##3
4. the indian is somewhere between the person eating potato and the person eating apple##7
5. the polish is somewhere to the left of the person eating apple##5
6. the indian is on the left or right of the polish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | plum    | potato   | garlic | apple  |
| Nationality   | german | polish | indian    | russian |

