.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, dutch, thai, british
4 different pets are kept: bird, goldfish, turtle, mouse
1. the dutch is not the owner of the mouse##6
2. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the owner of the mouse##3
3. the british is the owner of the turtle##1
4. the thai is somewhere between the british and the mexican##7
5. the dutch is on the left of the mexican##1
6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
7. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | british | thai | dutch | mexican |
| Pet           | turtle   | mouse    | bird       | goldfish  |

