.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, dancer, videographer, firefighter
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, soul, disco, house
1. the social-worker is not the fan of punk##6
2. the videographer is on the right of the social-worker##1
3. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the social-worker##3
4. the social-worker is on the right of the fan of house##1
5. the videographer is somewhere between the fan of house and the dancer##7
6. the fan of soul is somewhere to the right of the fan of disco##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Job           | firefighter | social-worker | videographer | dancer |
| Music-Genre   | house         | disco      | punk | soul            |

