.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, animation, disaster, epic
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rabbit, goldfish, chinchilla
1. the person watching epic movies is somewhere between the person watching fantasy movies and the owner of the chinchilla##7
2. the person watching animation movies is not the owner of the goldfish##6
3. the owner of the rabbit is not the person watching disaster movies##6
4. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
5. the person watching fantasy movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1
6. the person watching epic movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hedgehog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | epic | animation | disaster |
| Pet           | hedgehog    | rabbit   | chinchilla  | goldfish      |

