.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, time-travel, western, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, disco, dubstep, punk
1. the fan of punk is somewhere to the right of the fan of funk##5
2. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of funk##1
3. the fan of disco is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
4. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person watching horror movies is between the person watching time-travel movies and the fan of disco##2
6. the fan of dubstep is somewhere between the fan of disco and the person watching time-travel movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | horror | time-travel | western   |
| Music-Genre   | disco    | dubstep      | funk      | punk |

