3. the person who's sport is soccer is not the person who's hobby is drawing##6
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is basketball##5
6. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's hobby is camping##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
