.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: dancing, camping, drawing, card-games
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, helicopter, ship, boat
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person driving the ship is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the person driving the helicopter##6
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person driving the scooter and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
7. the person who's hobby is camping is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | card-games | dancing | camping | drawing |
| Transport   | scooter   | boat      | helicopter        | ship  |

