.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, juice, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, pop, country, salsa
1. the fan of pop is in an even position##4
2. the fan of salsa is somewhere between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the fan of country##7
3. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
4. the fan of country is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the fan of pop##5
6. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the fan of country##1
7. the person drinking tea is the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | sprite   | juice | tea | hot-chocolate   |
| Music-Genre   | funk | country   | salsa | pop |

