3. the dressmaker is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is not the dressmaker##6
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere between the fisherman and the journalist##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Hobby   | camping | magic-tricks     | woodworking     | gardening |
| Job     | dressmaker | journalist | musician | fisherman     |

