.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, chinchilla, lizard, frog
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, boat, airplane, taxi
1. the owner of the lizard is somewhere between the person driving the train and the owner of the chinchilla##7
2. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
3. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
4. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
5. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person driving the airplane##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | chinchilla    | lizard | frog     | cat |
| Transport   | airplane | taxi  | boat | train |

 